代香港四大產業之一的「產鹽業」，九龍灣鄰近的海域均為官方鹽場。因此官塘的「官」字即與「官方」有關。在1866年的《新安縣全圖》，在牛頭角與茶果嶺之間的海旁鄉村，寫為「官璫」；同期的《廣東水師營官兵駐房圖》則有「官檔」之名。有論者認為「璫」與「檔」均為誤傳。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/personal/%E8%A7%80%E5%A1%98%E5%AE%9A%E5%AE%98%E5%A1%98-%E6%96%B0%E4%B9%9D%E9%BE%8D%E8%A1%9B%E6%98%9F%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E4%BB%8B%E7%B4%B9/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpersonal%2F%25E8%25A7%2580%25E5%25A1%2598%25E5%25AE%259A%25E5%25AE%2598%25E5%25A1%2598-%25E6%2596%25B0%25E4%25B9%259D%25E9%25BE%258D%25E8%25A1%259B%25E6%2598%259F%25E5%259F%258E%25E5%25B8%2582%25E4%25BB%258B%25E7%25B4%25B9%2F&d=aLufatioEIfsHY%2FyaDEQJ2Abrlwo3OpfDsLQU8t9Jac%3D&h=d8b84ac6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpersonal%2F%25E8%25A7%2580%25E5%25A1%2598%25E5%25AE%259A%25E5%25AE%2598%25E5%25A1%2598-%25E6%2596%25B0%25E4%25B9%259D%25E9%25BE%258D%25E8%25A1%259B%25E6%2598%259F%25E5%259F%258E%25E5%25B8%2582%25E4%25BB%258B%25E7%25B4%25B9%2F&h=6e1e5ae8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/personal/%E8%A7%80%E5%A1%98%E5%AE%9A%E5%AE%98%E5%A1%98-%E6%96%B0%E4%B9%9D%E9%BE%8D%E8%A1%9B%E6%98%9F%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E4%BB%8B%E7%B4%B9/</a>"},{"pid":"cea75236cd69c08a1152839046cfa390a56a9df3","tid":2497160,"uid":154406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d5fe23abfce85699614232a941738d1938e84939","tid":2497160,"uid":393276,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b7e41560ea0ca1945c65159f3d28477a5e144ecf","tid":2497160,"uid":200200,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a9373ced3c52c700d4000d4d1cd8aca168115dbd","tid":2497160,"uid":177089,"like":19,"dislike":4,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T10:24:50.000Z","msg":"觀塘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n官塘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T10:36:49.000Z","msg":"紅van寫官塘係因為以前車頂D指示牌係人手寫出黎，個觀字太多筆劃<br />\n所以先用別字去代替"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021